Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Lesion of tendons/ligaments' from the indication dropdown menu
Then 'Add indication' button is enabled

And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
And 'Exclusion' radio button is enabled

And 'TFCC rupture/degeneration' checkbox is enabled
And 'SL dissociation' checkbox is enabled
And 'LT dissociation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ringband rupture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon rupture of the phalanges' checkbox is enabled
